{"tid":1331702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"數十人公眾席叫囂「反暴力、守護香港」　深水埗區議會會議流會","createTime":"2019-07-19T04:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T17:47:31.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91121b7406cac460d184072ba8ce666076c3304c","tid":1331702,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"// ... 深水埗今早舉行會議，議程上的討論事項除了要求在深水埗增建公營醫院、增撥資源改善社區環境衛生等民生項目，亦有區議員提出討論行政長官就《逃犯條例》修訂事件的回應，以及要求成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n會議期間，公眾席上有多名市民不停叫囂「反暴力、保民生」、「還社會安寧」、「不要家庭分裂」等口號，有人大叫「全世界都見到你們出賣祖國」，並有人高舉「沒有暴政只有暴徒」、「撤回政治草案，回歸民生議題」等標語。<br />\n<br />\n前警員、人稱「大波Man」的建制派人士石房有亦有到場 ... //<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/數十人公眾席叫囂-反暴力-守護香港-深水埗區議會會議流會/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E5%B8%AD%E5%8F%AB%E5%9B%82-%E5%8F%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E6%B5%81%E6%9C%83%2F&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=b2f7940f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E5%B8%AD%E5%8F%AB%E5%9B%82-%E5%8F%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E6%B5%81%E6%9C%83%2F&h=6a14c2d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/數十人公眾席叫囂-反暴力-守護香港-深水埗區議會會議流會/</a>"},{"pid":"f7ee7bcb1c8ef1ea9373eb985087ed1931c2aefa","tid":1331702,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGem6Rf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGem6Rf.png&h=b24b8c13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5pY84L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5pY84L.png